title: Bethel Music Discography 2002-2013 (11 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
BETHEL MUSIC DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 11 releases...

 * 2002 - Undone - Brian Johnson
 * 2009 - Here Is Love
 * 2010 - All I Have Needed - With Leah Mari
 * 2010 - Love Came Down - With Brian Johnson
 * 2011 - Be Lifted High - Live
 * 2011 - Hopes Anthem - With William Matthews
 * 2012 - For The Sake Of The World
 * 2012 - For The Sake Of The World - Single
 * 2012 - The Loft Sessions
 * 2013 - Tides
 * 2013 - Without Words

Over the past four years, Bethel Music has grown from a local church music ministry to a global outreach, featuring a cadre of songwriters and worship leaders, a half-dozen CDs, chart-topping songs such as "One Thing Remains," and both online and on-campus worship schools.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
